column1: This show yesterday was horrible. No one was dancing.
I liked some parts of the game and I did not enjoy others.
I woke up early to go swimming in the sea.
But these seaguls are nasty and grabbed my sandwich.
We should all celebrate this achievement of connecting ML endpoints with PowerBI.
Why are we not celebrating? I am feeling guilty about that.
I want our city to be free of corruption.
I am so excited. I reached 100000 subscribers on my Youtube channel.
Christoph and Marcel hope you had fun with the book so far.
